                <h3>About Me</h3>
                <p>
                I am a Sophomore at <a href="http://www.haverford.edu" target="_blank" >Haverford College</a>. I am going to major in Computer Science and Mathematics. My resume and github page are linked to above.
                You can probably guess that I like Computer Science and Mathematics. I also enjoy chess, reading fiction (short stories especially), martial arts (I've studied Tae-Kwan-Do), 
                reading and writing poetry and a bunch of other stuff that I don't feel like listing. In terms of programming, I am fond of C, C++ and am intrigued by functional programming languages.
                I am currently learning Scala and Haskell. I am interested in eventually learning some Scheme, Clojure, and Rust.

                </p>
