                <h3>Miscellaneous Cool Things</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        One of the things I am fiercely passionate about is education. I am highly critical of educational institutions and educational methodologies and philosophies. 
                        With one of my close friends, I made this awesome website called <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/torchlightwwp/" target="_blank">Torchlight</a> to remedy a major problem I saw at my school:
                        unequal distribution of information about the college system leading to inequality in opportunity. As for it's success, since my friend and I have been busy with college, we have been
                        unable to push it forward and spread it out. For now, only small circles in our high school are aware of the website. 
